Text: I have before but not for long, we’ve talked about me going to see someone and it looks like something I’m going to have to do soon

Author: simplyskyla
Text: I’m in the exact same situation...it’s so so hard because I want to get better but I just, just CAN’T. Have you tried seeing someone, maybe a psychiatrist or therapist? It will require patience and understanding from him but maybe if he sees that, it can help more
